              }
            ],
            "direction": "ltr",
            "format": "",
            "indent": 0,
            "type": "link",
            "rel": null,
            "target": null,
            "title": null,
            "url": "__GHOST_URL__/the-supreme-court-just-gave-corporations",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " in June. That radical opinion  — which has gone unmentioned in all the Roberts hagiographies — effectively barred retirees from suing when their employers let Wall Street firms bilk their pension funds. This was a huge win for both employers and the financial firms that drain retirement systems -- and it was a victory that came at exactly the moment the ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
